text: One of my favourite places for supper! Clean tables and quick service. Roti prata is pretty good here. Their teh o limau ice is a good companion to this meal.

Nice clean no-frills restaurant selling local Indian Muslim food. The pratas are fresh and the black chicken chop is hearty and flavourful. Prices are reasonable and place is surprisingly quiet on a Saturday evening. Place also shows EPL as well.
